N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7695.5 - Determinations by the department

State Regulations

Notwithstanding any other provision of this Part, nothing
shall prevent the department from making determinations pertaining thereto
consistent with legitimate penological objectives, and nothing contained herein
shall be deemed to grant any person any additional rights, privileges or cause
of action not otherwise granted or provided by law. Notes
